# Module: `packages/common`

- Shared utilities only — no UI, no canvas, no element logic
- No circular imports — this package must not import from other `@excalidraw/*` packages

## How to verify

- `grep -r "@excalidraw/" packages/common/` — should return nothing
- `grep -r "import.*react" packages/common/` — no UI/React imports expected
- `yarn build:packages` — circular imports cause build failures
